data.description: Stunning home in the highest point of sweet Hershey, nestled in Walton Spring Hills on 1.76 acres. Lovely 5 bedroom home with hardwood floors, cozy wood burning fireplace, crown molding and 2 stairwells. Spacious kitchen for entertaining family and friends with new flooring, leading out to a delightful deck and screened in porch. Upstairs, retreat to the peaceful primary bedroom suite with an oversized bonus room attached for crafts, extra closet or nursery including a balcony to enjoy the view of all seasons. Option to finish 3rd floor featuring a walk up staircase for a bedroom, movie theatre or game room(additional 1,000 sq ft). Lower level finished with new carpet and walk out basement. Built in shed attached to back of home for extra storage...the storage in this home is amazing! Beautiful backyard oasis with matured trees, wildlife, views of Ski Round top and Susquehanna River. Enjoy a cozy fire pit with smores and friends tucked away in the woods! Minutes to the medical center and major highways.
